## ‚ùå DON'T (Anti-patterns)

### Navigation Structure Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Too many items**: Don't exceed 7 main items
- ‚ùå **Unclear labels**: Don't use vague terms
- ‚ùå **Inconsistent placement**: Don't move navigation around
- ‚ùå **Hidden navigation**: Don't hide without clear trigger

