### Mobile Navigation Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Tiny tap targets**: Don't make items too small
- ‚ùå **Unclear menu icon**: Don't use unusual icons
- ‚ùå **No way to close**: Don't trap users
- ‚ùå **Hover-only menus**: Don't work on touch devices

### Dropdown Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Instant hover dropdowns**: Don't open immediately
- ‚ùå **Not keyboard accessible**: Don't ignore keyboard users
- ‚ùå **Too deep hierarchy**: Don't go beyond 2 levels
- ‚ùå **Close on hover-out**: Don't close too quickly

### Breadcrumb Mistakes
- ‚ùå **Missing on deep pages**: Don't omit when needed
- ‚ùå **Current page clickable**: Don't link to current page
- ‚ùå **Too long paths**: Don't show every level
- ‚ùå **Small touch targets**: Don't make links tiny

